                </p>
                <p><br />
                UPS 2nd Day Air: USA Service with Tracking Number<br />
  				Please Allow 2-4 Business Days for Delivery...Shipping &amp; Handling is calculated in Shopping Cart </p>
                <p>UPS 3 Day Select: USA Service with Tracking Number<br />
                Please Allow 3-5 Business Days for Delivery...Shipping &amp; Handling is calculated in Shopping Cart </p>
                <p>UPS Ground: USA Service with Tracking Number<br />
                Please Allow 7 Business Days for Delivery...Shipping &amp; Handling is calculated in Shopping Cart                 </p>
